funcs.doc:
Profiler is a convenient subrouter used for mounting net/http/pprof. ie.

	func MyService() http.Handler {
		r := chi.NewRouter()
		// ..middlewares
		r.Mount("/debug", middleware.Profiler())
		// ..routes
		return r
	}

